{"tid":1568260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係啊，係啊，手足比人打比人斬都冷處理","createTime":"2019-09-14T08:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T09:36:02.000Z","uid":66721,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"369e06603cb21ae52475c5ef1d0ceed335ef1ff6","tid":1568260,"uid":66721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:59:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌哂你地冷氣軍師老母</span><br />\n人地而家籃絲成群出動周圍打人<br />\n有手足比人拖出馬路<br />\n人地街坊都即刻出黎聲援<br />\n屌你地班連登仔叫人唔好出唔好理<br />\n比人踩到上心口都唔理，真係當手足係condom?<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/14/165332_bd38694a31ea81ec535d26551e0e6a2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F14%2F165332_bd38694a31ea81ec535d26551e0e6a2f.png&h=7dc0ddb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/14/165558_eaf12d93a0a79e4fb8d5c1f15d461217.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F14%2F165558_eaf12d93a0a79e4fb8d5c1f15d461217.png&h=ff000800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家見到依啲情況一定要跑返屋企開post叫人唔好出唔好送頭</span></span><br />\n屌你地老母連班廢老都搞唔掂話要推翻政府？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好撚失望</span></span>"},{"pid":"7b84478701ca48f0fe4ba88d5d35cbb5f34c1d9f","tid":1568260,"uid":279922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:01:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見到藍絲唔好再忍</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4a5d5dd0a2ba414a10fc3b4b5a0eccf248cb2b","tid":1568260,"uid":66721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:01:37.000Z","msg":"大家真係想幫手唔該街坊裝上陣救人，過左<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃金十分鐘</span>就好撤"},{"pid":"e2ce0366eb9d3b9b509bcda1b792a88ade942688","tid":1568260,"uid":66721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:03:27.000Z","msg":"見到人私了<br />\n唔該拉走大叫<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好啊，打死人啦</span></span></span> 既人<br />\n塞啲籃絲兩拳就hit and run"},{"pid":"ccea85c5648fd68e6819663b44adc74131c7100b","tid":1568260,"uid":201374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:06:13.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲都識見到人多就縮啦<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺唱榮光集會嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺組團修牆嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺大遊行嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為佢哋知自己吹雞唔夠人會俾人打返轉頭啊</span></span><br />\n連藍絲都識敵進我退,去淘大嗰班就唔識,明知冇PLAN好一定唔撚夠人都照衝,重蠢過藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔使再問遊行有警察係咪唔去<br />\n屌你咩每次遊行宣傳咗幾耐?有PLAN定有事前計劃咪會夠人囉,夠人咪去囉<br />\n朝早宣佈下晝有遊行,然後現場有幾百隻狗等你,你都唔撚去啦<br />\nbe water唔代表啲water識瞬間移動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日去淘大嗰班&quot;手足&quot;,同825嗰隻藍衫的士佬一樣咁戇鳩</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUkUVtU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUkUVtU.gif&h=8cdf3b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係以為藍絲企定定俾你打,以為自己可以一打十咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e1dcd9ad70227721411011c29856b65dc4bb34","tid":1568260,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:06:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>左膠仲話 唔好去啊 送頭啊 遲早無人再上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"63efbf6568282248008b7a0f35c738115beb2e5c","tid":1568260,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"記得敵進我退 be water<br />\n美國民主人權法要10月底左右先可能通過<br />\n依家係中共急, 唔係我地急<br />\n咁多挑引分化失敗post大家諗下係咪1毛出既<br />\n我地要be water, 長期戰阿"},{"pid":"7f5d863b49022419c199ca954e57489100f857ef","tid":1568260,"uid":66721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"仲見到有人罵手足送頭真係好撚燥<br />\n而家支那人佔左我地香港人商場仲比狗趕返我地香港人出黎<br />\n又選擇性執法，捉哂啲後生仔<br />\n支那人打完人就護送佢地走"},{"pid":"a2e92c56ded5abc4ccf972a293045f9ab9c5a254","tid":1568260,"uid":66721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63efbf6568282248008b7a0f35c738115beb2e5c","tid":1568260,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"記得敵進我退 be water<br />\n美國民主人權法要10月底左右先可能通過<br />\n依家係中共急, 唔係我地急<br />\n咁多挑引分化失敗post大家諗下係咪1毛出既<br />\n我地要be water, 長期戰阿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"真係要be water 但唔係有事發生即刻走<br />\n係吹雞快速反擊再走<br />\n如果唔係只會加劇破窗效應<br />\n更多手足係各區比人打<br />\n到時真係<span style=\"color: red;\">遍地開花</span>"},{"pid":"90c20382e82b31a3d00423f4d826ece6000fe502","tid":1568260,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRA52fJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRA52fJ.jpg&h=a63f7347&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fcdc8c2696150cda283de5c8a662a58bd8ae456","tid":1568260,"uid":66721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"仲話比人打完可以做文宣好材料<br />\n當比人打既手足係工具人？！"},{"pid":"aa3fb74f5c846c2fad212e4502abb200f4a9897d","tid":1568260,"uid":66721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"仲話比人打完可以做文宣好材料<br />\n當比人打既手足係工具人？！1"},{"pid":"24cecf4a4837579d879576cf21e84742939a7917","tid":1568260,"uid":66721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"